column5: and in honour of this event, I will be sending him a OFC hat and T-SHIRT!!
I wouldn't have waited so long for this tribute... I'd have given it to... oh say... the 23rd member!!!
Dang....I should of waited instead of buying that  hat, toque and t-shirt from Monique this summer!!
Congrats to you Randy! You'll be looking spiffy in the OFC gear. Keep them posts a comin'!
No offence to Crabbs but his member number is #4295...... rhcranked is #4000....  rhcranked Newbie Group: Members Posts: 3 Joined: 25-September 08 Member No.: 4,000   Burt
I noticed that too Burt!!!   ... maybe someone is padding the members list?

I understand your concern but this is how it works. When you register, you are assigned the next number on the list. If someone was to register under another name to have two accounts, one of the accounts would be dropped by administration.....so, the account numbers would continue to increase but the number of members would actually decrease. (as an example) That's why the account number is always greater than the actual number of members.  edit: We also do housecleaning from time to time to remove inactive accounts.
I just hope poor ol' rhcranked doesn't find out about this!... to learn that he's been living a lie for these past 3 1/2 months.. might be devastating!!!
ahhh come on be like dave ok everyone gets a T-SHIRT....LOL   ok maybe to many for that
Well, I think that all of the members from year 1 should get a hat and shirt!
